menuconfig SENSOR_EVENT_LOG
	bool "Sensor event console logger"
	depends on ZBUS
	depends on SENSOR_EVENT
	help
	  Subscribes a zbus listener to sensor_event_chan and logs every
	  env_sensor_data event to the console in a human-readable format:

	    [00:01:23.456]  0x1234  TEMP   23.45 °C
	    [00:01:23.456]  0x1234  HUM    65.2 %RH

	  No public API — enable with CONFIG_SENSOR_EVENT_LOG=y and the
	  library registers itself via SYS_INIT.
